      <h2>The Ancient Tea Standard</h2>
      <p>Greenie selects only the "1 bud 2 leaves" standard from trees confirmed at 200+ years of age. Each batch undergoes moisture analysis (target: ≤5%), visual inspection for oxidation consistency, and cupping by a certified tea taster before approval.</p>
      <p>Traditional withering on bamboo trays, hand-rolling in small batches, and oxidation monitored by artisans who learned the craft from their grandparents. No machine rolling, no artificial drying, no flavor additives.</p>

